# Layout patterns cheat-sheet

Common page / screen shapes. Fast reference for "how do I build a page that does X."

## Pattern — List + detail

```
[Sidebar list   ] [ Detail pane        ]
[ filter        ] [                    ]
[ item 1        ] [   selected item    ]
[ item 2        ] [                    ]
```

**When to use:** settings pages, inbox-style flows.
**Key components:** {{<Sidebar>_+_<DetailPane>_/_tailwind_grid_2-col}}

## Pattern — Dashboard

```
[ Top bar                         ]
[ Metric cards in row             ]
[ Primary chart        | Sidebar  ]
[ Secondary content    | charts   ]
```

**When to use:** analytics, overview screens.

## Pattern — Form flow

```
[ Step indicator      ]
[                     ]
[   Form fields       ]
[                     ]
[ [Cancel] [Continue] ]
```

**When to use:** onboarding, multi-step submission.

## Pattern — Empty state-first

```
[ Illustration      ]
[ Headline          ]
[ Supporting copy   ]
[ [Primary CTA]     ]
```

**When to use:** first-run experience, zero-data screens.

